rime-4-beyond"><em>《银河战士 Prime 4</em></a> 》预告片的推出。然而，FamiBoard 用户已经将 Tangerine Cookie 的预测提名为“ <a href="https://famiboards.com/threads/famiboards-shitpost-of-the-year-celebration-%E2%80%94-vote-ends-1-8-%E2%80%A2-see-threadmarks.12036/page-6#post-1507934" target="_blank" rel="noopener">年度最佳垃圾帖</a>”。</p><p> “这是官方消息，Reddit 子版块已经疯了，”一位用户在回应 Reddit 上分享的预测时<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/NintendoSwitch2/comments/1hunmpc/comment/m5ml41s/?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=web3x&amp;utm_name=web3xcss&amp;utm_term=1&amp;utm_content=share_button" target="_blank" rel="noopener">补充道</a>。</p><p>本周早些时候，据报道，一系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/heres-what-the-nintendo-switch-2-controller-could-look-like-3826408">泄露的图像证实了 Switch 2 的新控制器的外观</a>，这支持了之前泄露的有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/is-this-what-the-nintendo-switch-2-looks-like-3795099">新控制台比现有 Switch 更大、更强大的</a>信息。</p><p>还有消息称，PlayStation 热门小队射击游戏<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/helldivers-2">《Helldivers 2》</a></em>正在被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/helldivers-2-film-horizon-zero-dawn-3826692">改编成电影</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-fan-tarot-predict-switch-2-release-date-annoucement-3826719">任天堂粉丝使用塔罗牌预测 Switch 2 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
